    <title>hexo的使用指南</title>
    <link href="undefined2019/10/26/hexo%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/"/>
    <url>2019/10/26/hexo%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简写"><a href="#简写" class="headerlink" title="简写"></a>简写</h1><blockquote><p>hexo n “我的博客” == hexo new “我的博客” —–&gt;新建文章<br>hexo p == hexo publish<br>hexo g == hexo generate —-&gt;生成<br>hexo s == hexo server —–&gt; 启动服务预览<br>hexo d == hexo deploy —–&gt;部署到博客上</p></blockquote><h1 id="服务器"><a href="#服务器" class="headerlink" title="服务器"></a>服务器</h1><blockquote><p>hexo clean —&gt;清除缓存<br>hexo g —-&gt;生成静态网页<br>hexo d —-&gt;开始部署</p></blockquote><h1 id="监视文件变动"><a href="#监视文件变动" class="headerlink" title="监视文件变动"></a>监视文件变动</h1><blockquote><p>hexo generate –watch –&gt;监视文件变动</p></blockquote><h1 id="完成后部署"><a href="#完成后部署" class="headerlink" title="完成后部署"></a>完成后部署</h1><blockquote><p>hexo generate –deploy == hexo g -d<br>hexo deploy –generate == hexo d -g</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
